
= Development conventions =

== Test oriented development ==

Don't commit code which does not have it test.

This is a good read for everyone:

Start by reading this:

* http://petdance.com/perl/automated-testing/

Note: Test::Simple and Test::More are included in perl.

Reference card pdf:
http://pub.langworth.com/perl_test_refcard.pdf

This one goes a little bit further but nice to read
http://www.extremeperl.org/bk/unit-testing

- Code conventions